file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: My API
  description: My API
  termsOfService: https://hello.world/terms/
  contact:
    name: My API Owner
    email: myapi@example.com
    url: https://www.example.com
  license:
    name: My API. All rights reserved
    url: https://www.example.com
tags:
  - name: example
    description: example endpoints
paths:
  /example:
    get:
      tags:
        - example
      summary: Get example
      description: Get example
      operationId: getExample
      parameters:
        - in: header
          name: token
          description: Token
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Successful operation
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/ExampleResponse"
servers:
  - url: http://example.com/v1
components:
  parameters:
    tokenParam:
      in: header
      name: token
      description: Token
      required: false
      schema:
        type: string
  schemas:
    ExampleResponse:
      type: object
      required:
        - description
      properties:
        description:
          type: string
